Title: ['UAL']
Selftext: Should I Sell UAL and DAL
Upvote:
I bought UAL at $41 a share and DAL at $39. I've gained about 60% total profit on both of them combined. However, I'm not sure if they have much more in them, despite a lot of people getting the vaccine, I think it'll be a while more before air travel can get back go where it was. 
If I were to sell, I'd buy a bit of AMD, and some ETFs. Should I sell, or just continue to hold?
